2 likes, 0 comments - louisbothachildren on April 9, 2024: "Have you dreamt of your own custom made dress? This is your chance to WIN one 🤩

All the information you need:
👗Competition running from 1 September 2023 to 30 June 2024.
👗 R200 per ticket
👗Dress worth R15 000.00

You can email marketing1@jacarandachildren.co.za to purchase your tickets, otherwise just give us a call on 073 844 9266 / 012 800 4700

Tickets are available for purchase at Jakaranda Kinderhuis & Finders Keepers offices during office hours😁

Sponsors:
Custom-made dress:  Immagika Creative Designs 
Makeup : Viki Pienaar Professional Makeup Artist 
Hair : @dumanthair  Deon van Dyk (Stylist) / Juliette Smith (CEO)".
